Name: LH₂ Fill/Drain Line
Description: Vacuum-jacketed line for ground fill and drain operations
Key Specifications: diameter: 25 mm; material: SS316L; insulation: Vacuum-jacketed with MLI

Name: LH₂ Feed Line to Propulsion
Description: Main fuel feed line to propulsion system or fuel cell
Key Specifications: diameter: 50 mm; material: SS316L; insulation: Vacuum-jacketed with MLI

Name: Vent and Relief Line
Description: Pressure relief and emergency vent line
Key Specifications: diameter: 20 mm; material: SS316L; relief_pressure_setpoint: 8 bar

Name: Tank Mounting Struts
Description: Six G-10 fiberglass struts for tank mounting and load transfer
Key Specifications: number_of_struts: 6; material: G-10 fiberglass composite; load_capacity_per_strut: 5000 N (axial), 2000 N (lateral)

Name: Vacuum Jacket Support Ring
Description: Aluminum support ring for vacuum jacket outer shell
Key Specifications: material: Aluminum 6061-T6; diameter: 1200 mm; thickness: 10 mm

Name: Level Sensor Array
Description: Four capacitance-based level sensors for LH₂ level measurement
Key Specifications: number_of_sensors: 4; sensor_type: Capacitance-based; measurement_range: 0-100% tank height

Name: Temperature Sensor Array
Description: Eight platinum RTD sensors for temperature monitoring
Key Specifications: number_of_sensors: 8; sensor_type: Platinum RTD (Pt-100); measurement_range: -253°C to +85°C

Name: Pressure Transducers
Key Specifications: number_of_sensors: 3; sensor_type: Piezoresistive; measurement_range: 0-10 bar absolute

Name: Tank Control Unit CAN Bus
Description: CAN 2.0B bus for tank telemetry and commands
Key Specifications: protocol: CAN 2.0B; baud_rate: 500 kbps; connector: D-sub 9-pin

Name: MLI Vacuum Jacket Thermal Boundary
Description: Vacuum-jacketed MLI insulation boundary for cryogenic LH₂ storage
Key Specifications: insulation_system: 40-layer MLI (per INS-28-10-00-MLI-stack); reflector_material: Double-aluminized Mylar, 6.35 μm; spacer_material: Polyester netting
